xyz.softwaredeveloveper.impl

Class TimeStampLog<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.softwaredeveloveper.impl.TimeStampLog<T>

  • public class TimeStampLog<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores a collection of id's sorted by timestamp. Every value within the collection is associated to a timestamp.
